race.comment: I STOLE IT (1) has placed three of four over this track and trip and is much better than the recent outing suggests. Capable of bouncing back. CHAYSE 'N' LEISA (4) is a bit hit or miss but maps nicely for this from gate three and can feature if he brings her A-game. Former Victorian LA ROSETTA (12) is having her first run for the new yard but should find this easier than what she faced down south. Monitor market moves. ROCKRATA (22) won three back at this course and has since recorded two close seconds at Gatton and Ipswich. Holds each way appeal along with IRON GRACE (14) who was making late ground last start at the Gold Coast.
